<!-- ==================== DIAS ==================== -->
<Folder>
<name>📅 Dias (1-33)</name>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 1 — New York, NY</name>
<description>Dia 1 — Qui, 21/01
Chegada + Midtown leve 🗽
Chegada no JFK às 07h. Dia tranquilo pra se adaptar — tudo a pé em Midtown.

• 🏨 Check-in no Marriott Marquis (1535 Broadway, Times Square)
• 🎮 Nintendo NY (10 Rockefeller Plaza) — loja oficial, 2 andares de games!
• ⛪ St. Patrick's Cathedral (5th Ave com 50th St) — gratuita, linda por dentro
• 🧸 FAO Schwarz (30 Rockefeller Plaza) — loja de brinquedos icônica
• 🧱 LEGO Store (636 5th Ave) — maquetes gigantes de NY em LEGO</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ny</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-73.9855,40.758,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 2 — New York, NY</name>
<description>Dia 2 — Sex, 22/01
Downtown + Brooklyn + Chelsea 🌉
Dia intenso! WTC, Brooklyn Bridge, DUMBO, SoHo, High Line, Hudson Yards.

• ☕ Café no hotel ou próximo
• 👻 Ghostbusters Firehouse (14 North Moore St) — quartel real dos Caça-Fantasmas!
• 🏛️ Wall Street + Charging Bull + Fearless Girl
• ⛪ Oculus (WTC) — arquitetura de Calatrava impressionante
• 🕊️ 9/11 Memorial — piscinas nos locais das torres. Gratuito</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ny</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-73.9855,40.758,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 3 — New York, NY</name>
<description>Dia 3 — Sab, 23/01
Central Park + Chinatown + Downtown 🌳
Norte → Sul! Central Park, depois desce: Chinatown, Little Italy, Katz's.

• 🌳 Central Park — Strawberry Fields, Bethesda Fountain, Bow Bridge
• 🏛️ MET (opcional ~2h) — na 82nd com 5th! Ingresso ~$30
• 🏨 The Plaza Hotel — hotel do Kevin em Esqueceram de Mim 2!
• 🏮 Chinatown — Canal St + Mott St, a maior dos EUA!
• 🍝 Little Italy — Mulberry St. Cannoli na Ferrara Bakery (desde 1892!)</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ny</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-73.9855,40.758,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 4 — New York, NY</name>
<description>Dia 4 — Dom, 24/01
Mirante + Flatiron + Despedida 🏙️
Último dia em NY. Roosevelt Island, Summit, Grand Central, Flatiron.

• 🚡 Roosevelt Island Tramway (59th St com 2nd Ave) — bondinho aéreo! $2.90
• 🏙️ Summit One Vanderbilt (45 E 42nd St) — mirante imersivo de espelhos! ~1.5h
• 🚶 Grand Central Terminal — teto estrelado, relógio de opala
• 🏢 Flatiron Building (23rd St) — prédio triangular de 1902!
• 🎮 Voltar na Nintendo NY ou explorar algo novo</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ny</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-73.9855,40.758,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 5 — New York → LAX → Las Vegas</name>
<description>Dia 5 — Seg, 25/01
NY → LA → Vegas! ✈️🚗
Check-out do Marriott, voo pro LAX, Tesla e direto pra Vegas!

• ☕ Café no Marriott Marquis
• 🏨 Check-out
• Chegada no JFK — check-in / despachar malas
• 🎰 Chegada em Las Vegas! Check-in
• 🏨 Dormir cedo (jet lag + dia longo!)</description>
<styleUrl>#day-nv</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-115.1398,36.1699,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 6 — Welcome Sign + Mt. Charleston</name>
<description>Dia 6 — Ter, 26/01
Neve a 45 min de Vegas! 🏔️
Foto no Welcome Sign de manhã + neve em Mt. Charleston!

• ☕ Café
• 📸 Welcome to Las Vegas Sign — foto icônica!
• 🏔️ Kyle Canyon Scenic Drive — neve nas montanhas!
• ⛄ Parada — brincar na neve! Boneco de neve, guerra de bolas!
• 🏨 Explorar hotéis — Venetian (canais), Bellagio (conservatório), Caesars Palace</description>
<styleUrl>#day-nv</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-115.1398,36.1699,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 7 — Valley of Fire + Strip</name>
<description>Dia 7 — Qua, 27/01
Parque mais fotogênico de Nevada! 🔥
Fire Wave + Elephant Rock de manhã, tarde livre na Strip.

• 🔥 Valley of Fire — arenito vermelho surreal!
• 🥾 Fire Wave Trail (~2 km) — ondas de rocha listrada!
• 📸 Elephant Rock
• 📸 White Domes Trail (~1.8 km) — cânion colorido
• Tempo livre — descanso, piscina, explorar a Strip</description>
<styleUrl>#day-nv</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-115.1398,36.1699,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 8 — Day trip Death Valley 🏜️</name>
<description>Dia 8 — Qui, 28/01
Ponto mais baixo das Américas!
Última noite em Vegas! Inverno é a melhor época pra Death Valley.

• ☕ Café
• ⬇️ Badwater Basin — ponto mais baixo das Américas (-86m)!
• 🚗 Artist's Drive + Artist's Palette — montanhas coloridas
• 🏜️ Devil's Golf Course — cristais de sal!
• 📸 Zabriskie Point — formações douradas</description>
<styleUrl>#day-nv</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-115.1398,36.1699,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 9 — Vegas → Grand Canyon → Zion</name>
<description>Dia 9 — Sex, 29/01
GC de tarde + Zion à noite! 🏜️
Dia longo (~700 km) mas épico — GC à tarde é suficiente!

• ☕ Café + check-out de Vegas
• 🏗️ Hoover Dam — mirante na US-93! Ponte Memorial com vista da barragem a 270m acima do Rio Colorado!
• 🛣️ Hackberry General Store — posto vintage da Route 66 com Corvette clássico!
• 🏚️ Seligman — 'Berço da Route 66'! Inspiração de Radiator Springs do filme Carros da Pixar!
• 🏜️ Chegada no Grand Canyon!</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ut</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-112.1401,36.0544,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 10 — Zion NP dia cheio</name>
<description>Dia 10 — Sab, 30/01
Trilhas, mirantes e pôr do sol! 🏞️
Dia cheio em Zion! No inverno pode dirigir no canyon (sem shuttle).

• ☕ Café em Springdale
• 🥾 Watchman Trail (~5 km, ~2h) — vista panorâmica!
• 🥾 Emerald Pools Trail (Lower + Upper, ~4 km)
• 📸 Court of the Patriarchs
• 🛍️ Explorar Springdale</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ut</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-112.9871,37.209,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 11 — Zion AM → Bryce PM</name>
<description>Dia 11 — Dom, 31/01
Última manhã em Zion + Bryce à tarde! 🏔️
Navajo Loop + pôr do sol + stargazing em Bryce!

• ☕ Café
• 🥾 Riverside Walk
• 📸 Últimas fotos em Zion
• 🏁 Checkerboard Mesa — arenito com padrão xadrez natural! Pullover na UT-9
• 🛣️ Red Canyon — arcos vermelhos na estrada!</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ut</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-112.1677,37.6283,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 12 — Bryce → Moab</name>
<description>Dia 12 — Seg, 01/02
Nascer do sol em Bryce + Corona Arch! 🏜️
Sunrise épico, depois estrada até Moab.

• 🌅 Nascer do sol em Bryce Point!
• ☕ Café + check-out
• 🌄 Head of the Rocks Overlook — mirante da UT-12 com vista épica de Escalante!
• 🏜️ Capitol Reef NP — paredões vermelhos! Petroglífos Fremont de 2.000 anos + Fruita Historic District
• 👽 Goblin Valley State Park — formações em forma de cogumelos/aliens! Parece outro planeta!</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ut</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-109.5498,38.5733,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 13 — Canyonlands NP dia cheio 🏜️</name>
<description>Dia 13 — Ter, 02/02
Island in the Sky — cânions infinitos!
Mesa Arch ao nascer do sol — o sol nasce ATRAVÉS do arco!

• ☕ Café cedo
• 🌅 Mesa Arch ao nascer do sol — o arco mais fotografado de Utah!
• 📸 Grand View Point — cânions infinitos!
• 📸 Green River Overlook
• 🏞️ Shafer Canyon Overlook</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ut</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-109.5498,38.5733,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 14 — Arches NP + Dead Horse Point</name>
<description>Dia 14 — Qua, 03/02
Delicate Arch + Dead Horse sunset! 🏜️
O arco mais famoso do mundo + vista sobre o Colorado!

• ☕ Café
• 🏞️ Entrada em Arches NP
• 🥾 Delicate Arch Trail (~5 km, ~2-3h) — o arco mais famoso!
• 📸 Windows Section — North/South Window, Turret Arch
• 📸 Double Arch</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ut</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-109.5498,38.5733,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 15 — Moab → Antelope Island → Twin Falls</name>
<description>Dia 15 — Qui, 04/02
Bisões + Shoshone Falls + Evel Knievel! 🦬
Dia longo — bisões na Antelope Island + Shoshone Falls + local do salto do Evel Knievel!

• ☕ Café + check-out
• 🦬 Antelope Island SP — bisões selvagens + Great Salt Lake!
• 📸 Buffalo Point — mirante 360°
• � Perrine Bridge — ponte sobre o Snake River Canyon! Ponto de BASE jumping legal 🪂
• 📸 Evel Knievel Jump Site — local do famoso salto de 1974 sobre o Snake River Canyon!</description>
<styleUrl>#day-pnw</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-111.891,40.7608,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 16 — Twin Falls → Multnomah → Centralia</name>
<description>Dia 16 — Sex, 05/02
Columbia Gorge + Multnomah Falls! 💧
Dia de transição longo — cachoeira icônica de 189m!

• ☕ Café + check-out
• 📸 Deadman Pass Overlook — mirante nas Blue Mountains! Vista panorâmica a 1.278m de altitude
• �️ (opcional) Mt. Hood — desvio ~1h ao sul pela US-26. Vulcão de 3.429m coberto de neve!
• 🏞️ (opcional) Trillium Lake — lago com reflexo perfeito do Mt. Hood! Ótimo pra fotos
• �🏞️ Columbia River Gorge</description>
<styleUrl>#day-pnw</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-121,45.5,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 17 — Centralia → Mt. Rainier → Forks</name>
<description>Dia 17 — Sab, 06/02
Vulcão Rainier + Olympic NP! 🌋
Rainier de manhã, Lake Crescent e Sol Duc Falls à tarde!

• ☕ Café + check-out
• 🌋 Mt. Rainier — Paradise! Vulcão de 4.392m coberto de neve!
• ⛄ Brincar na neve! Boneco de neve, guerra de bolas, sled (~45 min)
• 📸 Fotos do vulcão — se o céu estiver limpo, vista espetacular!
• 🚶 Caminhar pela área de Paradise na neve</description>
<styleUrl>#day-pnw</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-123.5,47,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 18 — Olympic NP dia cheio 🌲</name>
<description>Dia 18 — Dom, 07/02
Florestas místicas + praias selvagens!
Hoh Rain Forest + Ruby Beach + Twilight!

• ☕ Café
• 🌲 Hoh Rain Forest — floresta tropical temperada!
• 🥾 Hall of Mosses Trail (~1.3 km) — musgos pendurados!
• 🥾 Spruce Nature Trail (~2 km)
• 🌊 Ruby Beach — sea stacks!</description>
<styleUrl>#day-pnw</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-124.3855,47.9504,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 19 — Forks → Cannon Beach</name>
<description>Dia 19 — Seg, 08/02
Astoria + Haystack Rock ao pôr do sol! 🌅
Cidade do Goonies + pôr do sol mais bonito da viagem!

• ☕ Café + check-out de Forks
• 🌳 Kalaloch Tree of Life — árvore crescendo sobre caverna com raízes expostas como tentáculos!
• 🏖️ Cape Disappointment — farol no encontro do Rio Columbia com o Pacífico!
• 🚢 Peter Iredale Shipwreck — naufrágio de 1906 na praia! Esqueleto do navio visível!
• 🌊 Astoria — cenário de The Goonies! Astoria Column!</description>
<styleUrl>#day-pnw</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-123.9615,45.8918,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 20 — Costa Oregon Sul</name>
<description>Dia 20 — Ter, 09/02
Thor's Well + faróis + Samuel Boardman! 🌊
O melhor dia de costa — 350 km de paradas espetaculares!

• ☕ Café + última caminhada em Cannon Beach
• 📸 Cape Perpetua + Thor's Well
• 🏖️ Heceta Head Lighthouse
• 🦌 Dean Creek Elk Viewing Area — manada de Roosevelt elk selvagens!
• 📸 Shore Acres State Park</description>
<styleUrl>#day-pnw</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-124.2179,43.3665,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 21 — Redwood NP norte — Jedediah Smith! 🌲</name>
<description>Dia 21 — Qua, 10/02
Jedediah Smith + Crescent City! 🌲
Dia tranquilo entre redwoods perto de Crescent City.

• ☕ Café + check-out de Gold Beach
• 🌲 Jedediah Smith Redwoods SP — Stout Memorial Grove Trail (~1 km loop entre gigantes!)
• 🚗 Howland Hill Road — estrada de terra entre redwoods enormes
• 🥾 Boy Scout Tree Trail (~4 km) — trilha tranquila entre old-growth
• 🏨 Check-in Crescent City</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ca</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-124.2026,41.7558,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 22 — Redwood NP sul → Eureka</name>
<description>Dia 22 — Qui, 11/02
Fern Canyon + Tall Trees + Avenue of Giants! 🌲
Tudo descendo ao sul — sem backtrack! Fern Canyon, Tall Trees e Avenue of Giants.

• ☕ Café + check-out de Crescent City
• 🚗 Newton B. Drury Scenic Parkway
• 📸 Big Tree Wayside
• 🥾 Fern Canyon (~1.5 km) — samambaias! Jurassic Park 2!
• 🌊 Gold Bluffs Beach</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ca</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-124.1637,40.8021,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 23 — Eureka → San Francisco</name>
<description>Dia 23 — Sex, 12/02
Point Reyes + baleias + SF! 🐋
Alces selvagens, baleias cinzentas e Golden Gate!

• ☕ Café + check-out de Eureka
• 🏖️ Glass Beach (Fort Bragg) — praia coberta de vidro marítimo polido pelas ondas!
• 🌊 Mendocino — vila costeira charmosa, cenário de filmes! Parada rápida
• 🐋 Point Reyes — Elk Preserve, Lighthouse + baleias cinzentas! (migração jan-abr!)
• 🏨 Chegada em SF! Check-in</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ca</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-122.4194,37.7749,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 24 — San Francisco dia cheio 1</name>
<description>Dia 24 — Sab, 13/02
Pier 39 + Golden Gate + Nintendo! 🌉
Cable Car, Chinatown, Golden Gate Bridge, Nintendo SF!

• ☕ Café
• 🏖️ Pier 39 — leões-marinhos!
• 🚋 Passeio de Cable Car
• 🌆 Lombard Street
• 🏮 Chinatown de SF — a mais antiga dos EUA!</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ca</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-122.4194,37.7749,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 25 — San Francisco — Valentine's Day! ❤️</name>
<description>Dia 25 — Dom, 14/02
Alcatraz + Golden Gate Park + Valentine's! ❤️
Valentine's Day! Alcatraz de manhã, Golden Gate Park e jantar especial à noite!

• ☕ Café
• 🏝️ Alcatraz — ferry Pier 33 (~2h na ilha)
• 🚢 Ferry de volta
• 🌳 Golden Gate Park — Japanese Tea Garden, Conservatory of Flowers
• 🎨 Mission District — murais, Painted Ladies (Alamo Square)</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ca</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-122.4194,37.7749,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 26 — San Francisco dia cheio 3</name>
<description>Dia 26 — Seg, 15/02
Golden Gate + Fisherman's Wharf! 🌉
Mais um dia em SF — Golden Gate, Painted Ladies, Chinatown!

• ☕ Café
• 🌉 Golden Gate Bridge — caminhada + fotos!
• 🏞️ Battery Spencer — vista icônica da ponte!
• 🦞 Fisherman's Wharf + Pier 39 — leões-marinhos!
• 🚋 Cable Car (Powell-Hyde line)</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ca</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-122.4194,37.7749,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 27 — SF → PCH → Yosemite</name>
<description>Dia 27 — Ter, 16/02
Bixby Bridge + drive pra Yosemite! 🌊🏔️
PCH de manhã, depois corta pro interior rumo a Yosemite!

• ☕ Café + check-out de SF
• 🏖️ Parada rápida em Half Moon Bay
• 🦞 Cannery Row — passear + café
• 🚗 17-Mile Drive — Lone Cypress, Pebble Beach!
• 🌉 Bixby Creek Bridge — foto icônica!</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ca</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-121.9,36.6,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 28 — Yosemite NP dia 1 — Valley</name>
<description>Dia 28 — Qua, 17/02
Tunnel View + cachoeiras + neve! 🏞️
Primeiro dia em Yosemite! Valley com neve — lindo!

• ☕ Café em Mariposa
• 📸 Tunnel View — vista icônica: El Capitan + Half Dome + Bridalveil!
• 🌊 Bridalveil Fall — trilha curta ~10 min
• 🏔️ El Capitan Meadow — paredão de 900m!
• 🌊 Yosemite Falls — Lower trail ~30 min — pode ter gelo!</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ca</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-119.5383,37.8651,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 29 — Yosemite NP dia 2 — Neve!</name>
<description>Dia 29 — Qui, 18/02
Badger Pass + trilhas na neve! ⛷️
Snow tubing, snowshoeing e mais Yosemite Valley!

• ☕ Café em Mariposa
• ⛷️ Badger Pass Ski Area — snow tubing! Perfeito pra família!
• 🏔️ Snowshoeing guiado pelo ranger (grátis, ~2h)
• 🌲 Cook's Meadow Loop — trilha fácil, Half Dome + Yosemite Falls com neve
• 📸 Revisitar favoritos — luz diferente da tarde!</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ca</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-119.5383,37.8651,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 30 — Mariposa → Kings Canyon → Sequoia</name>
<description>Dia 30 — Sex, 19/02
General Sherman + Moro Rock! 🌲
Dia inteiro entre as maiores árvores do mundo!

• ☕ Café + check-out de Mariposa
• 🌲 General Grant Tree — 2ª maior sequoia do mundo!
• 🌲 North Grove Loop (~1 km) — floresta de sequoias gigantes!
• 🌲 General Sherman Tree — a MAIOR árvore do mundo! 84m!
• 🥾 Congress Trail (~3 km loop) — entre sequoias gigantes</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ca</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-118.751,36.564,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 31 — Three Rivers → Los Angeles</name>
<description>Dia 31 — Sab, 20/02
Tehachapi Loop + rumo a LA! 🚗
Último dia de estrada! Parada no Tehachapi Loop, depois praias de LA.

• ☕ Café + check-out de Three Rivers
• 🛤️ Tehachapi Loop — famoso loop ferroviário!
• 🏨 Chegada em LA! Check-in
• 🏖️ Santa Monica Pier — roda-gigante, Route 66 End Sign!
• 🌴 Venice Beach — boardwalk, Muscle Beach!</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ca</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-118.2437,34.0522,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 32 — LA dia cheio</name>
<description>Dia 32 — Dom, 21/02
Hollywood + Griffith Observatory! 🎬
Último dia completo nos EUA!

• ☕ Café
• ⭐ Hollywood Walk of Fame + TCL Chinese Theatre
• 📸 Hollywood Sign — vista do Griffith Observatory trail
• 🔭 Griffith Observatory — vista panorâmica de LA!
• 🎬 Universal Studios Hollywood OU passeio livre (compras, Beverly Hills)</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ca</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-118.2437,34.0522,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
<Placemark>
<name>Dia 33 — LA → Voo de volta ✈️</name>
<description>Dia 33 — Seg, 22/02
Dia da volta! 🇧🇷
Devolução do Tesla + voo MIA → GIG.

• ☕ Café + check-out
• 🛍️ Manhã livre — compras de última hora
• Chegada no LAX — check-in
• 🛍️ Últimas compras duty free
• Chegada em Miami</description>
<styleUrl>#day-ca</styleUrl>
<Point><coordinates>-118.2437,34.0522,0</coordinates></Point>
</Placemark>
</Folder>

